dcterms:description: TB-Dense is a densely annotated dataset for Event Temporal Relation Classification (ETRC) that annotates the temporal relations of pairs of events across sentences, including six temporal relations: AFTER, BEFORE, INCLUDE, IS INCLUDED, VAGUE, and SIMULTANEOUS.
dcterms:title: TB-Dense

dcterms:creator: Qiang Ning
Hao Wu
Dan Roth
dcterms:description: MATRES is a refined dataset that uses a multi-axis annotation scheme for event temporal relations, containing four temporal relations: BEFORE, AFTER, EQUAL, and VAGUE, and is based on 275 documents from TimeBank and TempEval.
dcterms:title: MATRES
